article.description: — Keshon Gilbert scored 13 points as UNLV beat Southern 66-56 on Monday night in a season opener.
article.headline: Gilbert scores 13, UNLV knocks off Southern 66-56
article.linkText: Gilbert scores 13, UNLV knocks off Southern 66-56
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Keshon Gilbert scored 13 points as UNLV beat Southern 66-56 on Monday night in a season opener. Elijah Harkless scored 11 points and Jackie Johnson III finished with 10 points. Bryson Etienne had 25 points for the Jaguars. NEXT UP Up next for UNLV is a Saturday matchup with Incarnate Word at home. Southern visits Arizona on Friday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
